#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.68"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.68:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.68:0.2"
msgid "7. Mahāvagga"
msgstr "7. The Great Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.68:0.3"
msgid "68. Kosambisutta"
msgstr "68. At Kosambī"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
#. VAR: musilo → mūsīlo (bj) | musīlo (pts1-2)
#. VAR: paviṭṭho → saviṭṭho (bj, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn12.68:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ āyasmā ca musilo āyasmā ca paviṭṭho āyasmā ca nārado āyasmā ca "
"ānando kosambiyaṃ viharanti ghositārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the venerables Musīla, Saviṭṭha, Nārada, and Ānanda were staying "
"near Kosambī in Ghosita’s monastery."

msgctxt "sn12.68:1.2"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā paviṭṭho āyasmantaṃ musilaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Saviṭṭha said to Venerable Musila:"

msgctxt "sn12.68:1.3"
msgid ""
"“aññatreva, āvuso musila, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato musilassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Musila, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:1.4"
msgid "‘jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’”ti?"
msgstr "rebirth is a condition for old age and death?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:1.6"
msgid "‘jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’”ti."
msgstr "rebirth is a condition for old age and death.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.116"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso musila, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato musilassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Musila, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.2"
msgid "‘bhavapaccayā jātīti … pe …"
msgstr "continued existence is a condition for rebirth …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.3"
msgid "upādānapaccayā bhavoti …"
msgstr "grasping is a condition for continued existence …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.4"
msgid "taṇhāpaccayā upādānanti …"
msgstr "craving is a condition for grasping …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.5"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhāti …"
msgstr "feeling is a condition for craving …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.6"
msgid "phassapaccayā vedanāti …"
msgstr "contact is a condition for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.7"
msgid "saḷāyatanapaccayā phassoti …"
msgstr "the six sense fields are conditions for contact …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.8"
msgid "nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatananti …"
msgstr "name and form are conditions for the six sense fields …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.9"
msgid "viññāṇapaccayā nāmarūpanti …"
msgstr "consciousness is a condition for name and form …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.10"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇanti …"
msgstr "choices are a condition for consciousness …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.11"
msgid "avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’”ti?"
msgstr "ignorance is a condition for choices?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.12"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:2.13"
msgid "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’”ti."
msgstr "ignorance is a condition for choices.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:3.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso musila, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato musilassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Musila, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:3.2"
msgid "‘jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’”ti?"
msgstr "when rebirth ceases, old age and death cease?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:3.3"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:3.4"
msgid "‘jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’”ti."
msgstr "when rebirth ceases, old age and death cease.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.117"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:4.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso musila, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato musilassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Musila, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.2"
msgid "‘bhavanirodhā jātinirodhoti … pe …"
msgstr "when continued existence ceases, rebirth ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.3"
msgid "upādānanirodhā bhavanirodhoti …"
msgstr "when grasping ceases, continued existence ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.4"
msgid "taṇhānirodhā upādānanirodhoti …"
msgstr "when craving ceases, grasping ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.5"
msgid "vedanānirodhā taṇhānirodhoti …"
msgstr "when feeling ceases, craving ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.6"
msgid "phassanirodhā vedanānirodhoti …"
msgstr "when contact ceases, feeling ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.7"
msgid "saḷāyatananirodhā phassanirodhoti …"
msgstr "when the six sense fields cease, contact ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.8"
msgid "nāmarūpanirodhā saḷāyatananirodhoti …"
msgstr "when name and form cease, the six sense fields cease …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.9"
msgid "viññāṇanirodhā nāmarūpanirodhoti …"
msgstr "when consciousness ceases name and form cease …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.10"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodhoti …"
msgstr "when choices cease consciousness ceases …"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.11"
msgid "avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’”ti?"
msgstr "when ignorance ceases, choices cease?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.12"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:4.13"
msgid "‘avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’”ti."
msgstr "when ignorance ceases, choices cease.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:5.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso musila, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato musilassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Musila, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:5.2"
msgid "‘bhavanirodho nibbānan’”ti?"
msgstr "the cessation of continued existence is extinguishment?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:5.3"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:5.4"
msgid "‘bhavanirodho nibbānan’”ti."
msgstr "the cessation of continued existence is extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:6.1"
msgid "“Tenahāyasmā musilo arahaṃ khīṇāsavo”ti?"
msgstr "“Then Venerable Musila is a perfected one, with defilements ended.”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:6.2"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā musilo tuṇhī ahosi."
msgstr "When he said this, Musila kept silent."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:7.1"
msgid "Atha kho āyasmā nārado āyasmantaṃ paviṭṭhaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Then Venerable Nārada said to Venerable Saviṭṭha:"

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.2"
msgid "“sādhāvuso paviṭṭha, ahaṃ etaṃ pañhaṃ labheyyaṃ."
msgstr "“Reverend Saviṭṭha, please let me answer these questions."

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.3"
msgid "Maṃ etaṃ pañhaṃ puccha."
msgstr "Ask me"

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.4"
msgid "Ahaṃ te etaṃ pañhaṃ byākarissāmī”ti."
msgstr "and I will answer them for you.”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.5"
msgid "“Labhatāyasmā nārado etaṃ pañhaṃ."
msgstr "“By all means, Venerable Nārada, try these questions."

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.6"
msgid "Pucchāmahaṃ āyasmantaṃ nāradaṃ etaṃ pañhaṃ."
msgstr "I’ll ask you"

msgctxt "sn12.68:7.7"
msgid "Byākarotu ca me āyasmā nārado etaṃ pañhaṃ."
msgstr "and you can answer them for me.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:8.1"
msgid ""
"Aññatreva, āvuso nārada, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato nāradassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"(Saviṭṭha repeats exactly the same series of questions, and Nārada answers "
"just as Musila did.)"

msgctxt "sn12.68:8.2"
msgid "‘jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:8.3"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:8.4"
msgid "‘jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇan’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:9.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso nārada, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato nāradassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:9.2"
msgid "bhavapaccayā jāti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:9.3"
msgid "avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:9.4"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:9.5"
msgid "‘avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:10.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso nārada, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato nāradassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:10.2"
msgid "‘jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:10.3"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:10.4"
msgid "‘jātinirodhā jarāmaraṇanirodho’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:11.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso nārada, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato nāradassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:11.2"
msgid "‘bhavanirodhā jātinirodhoti … pe …"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:11.3"
msgid "avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:11.4"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn12.68:11.5"
msgid "‘avijjānirodhā saṅkhāranirodho’”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:12.1"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso nārada, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā atthāyasmato nāradassa "
"paccattameva ñāṇaṃ:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Nārada, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, do you "
"know for yourself that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:12.2"
msgid "‘bhavanirodho nibbānan’”ti?"
msgstr "the cessation of continued existence is extinguishment?”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:12.3"
msgid ""
"“Aññatreva, āvuso paviṭṭha, saddhāya aññatra ruciyā aññatra anussavā aññatra "
"ākāraparivitakkā aññatra diṭṭhinijjhānakkhantiyā ahametaṃ jānāmi ahametaṃ "
"passāmi:"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, apart from faith, personal preference, oral tradition, "
"reasoned contemplation, or acceptance of a view after consideration, I know "
"and see that"

msgctxt "sn12.68:12.4"
msgid "‘bhavanirodho nibbānan’”ti."
msgstr "the cessation of continued existence is extinguishment.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.118"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:13.1"
msgid "“Tenahāyasmā nārado arahaṃ khīṇāsavo”ti?"
msgstr "“Then Venerable Nārada is a perfected one, with defilements ended.”"

msgctxt "sn12.68:13.2"
msgid ""
"“‘Bhavanirodho nibbānan’ti kho me, āvuso, yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"sudiṭṭhaṃ, na camhi arahaṃ khīṇāsavo."
msgstr ""
"“I have truly seen clearly with right wisdom that the cessation of continued "
"existence is extinguishment. Yet I am not a perfected one."

msgctxt "sn12.68:13.3"
msgid ""
"Seyyathāpi, āvuso, kantāramagge udapāno, tatra nevassa rajju na udakavārako."
msgstr ""
"Suppose there was a well on a desert road that had neither rope nor bucket."

msgctxt "sn12.68:13.4"
msgid ""
"Atha puriso āgaccheyya ghammābhitatto ghammapareto kilanto tasito pipāsito, "
"so taṃ udapānaṃ olokeyya."
msgstr ""
"Then along comes a person struggling in the oppressive heat, weary, thirsty, "
"and parched."

msgctxt "sn12.68:13.5"
msgid "Tassa ‘udakan’ti hi kho ñāṇaṃ assa, na ca kāyena phusitvā vihareyya."
msgstr ""
"They’d know that there was water, but they couldn’t physically touch it."

msgctxt "sn12.68:13.6"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho, āvuso, ‘bhavanirodho nibbānan’ti yathābhūtaṃ sammappaññāya "
"sudiṭṭhaṃ, na camhi arahaṃ khīṇāsavo”ti."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, I have truly seen clearly with right wisdom that the "
"cessation of continued existence is extinguishment. Yet I am not a perfected "
"one.”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.68:14.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, āyasmā ānando āyasmantaṃ paviṭṭhaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "When he said this, Venerable Ānanda said to Venerable Saviṭṭha:"

#. VAR: evaṃvādī → evaṃvādiṃ (?)
msgctxt "sn12.68:14.2"
msgid "“evaṃvādī tvaṃ, āvuso paviṭṭha, āyasmantaṃ nāradaṃ kiṃ vadesī”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Saviṭṭha, what do you have to say to Venerable Nārada when he "
"speaks like this?”"

# See BB for notes on the reading. I don’t understand why BB translates “about” here. Normally the accusative is when you speak “to” someone, and as Narada is right there, why would it mean anything else?
msgctxt "sn12.68:14.3"
msgid ""
"“Evaṃvādāhaṃ, āvuso ānanda, āyasmantaṃ nāradaṃ na kiñci vadāmi aññatra "
"kalyāṇā aññatra kusalā”ti."
msgstr ""
"“Reverend Ānanda, I have nothing to say to Venerable Nārada when he speaks "
"like this, except what is good and wholesome.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.68:14.4"
msgid "Aṭṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
